                                <item xml:id="a4" corresp="#h3">
                                    <locus from="2v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT2810RepCh94" type="complete"/>. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ኦእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እሙ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስ፡ ከሃሊ</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a5" corresp="#h3">
                                    <locus from="3r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT2970RepCh251" type="complete"/>. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">በሰጊድ፡ ስብሐት፡ ዘመዓዛ፡ ስምከ፡ አፈዋት፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ቅቡዕ፡ ዘአልባስጥሮስ፡ ዕፍረት፤ ሀገረ፡ ዳዊት፡ ለቤዛ፡ ነፍሳት፡ </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a6">
                                    <locus from="4r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT1968Mashaf" type="complete"/>
                           </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a7">
                                    <locus from="6r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT3993Miracle" type="complete"/>
                           </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a8">
                                    <locus from="8r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The note states that the manuscript belongs to the church of <placeName ref="INS0101MadhaneAlam"/>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘ<placeName ref="INS0101MadhaneAlam">ቅ'፡ 
                                        መ'፡ ዓለም።</placeName>
                           </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a9">
                                    <locus target="#177v"/>
                                    <date when="1663"/>
                                    <desc type="LandGrant">Deed of gift by <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada"/> of certain lands, the following the the recipient:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ቤተ፡ ክርስተያነ፡ አእዳወ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እኅወ፡ ኢ ፲ቤጌ፡ አባ፡ ዘክርስቶስ፡ ^ወልደ፡ አባለ፡ ክ ርስቶስ፡</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a10">
                                    <locus from="177v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT3065RepCh345" type="incomplete"/>, the end is missing. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦዑጽፍተ፡ ልብሰ፡ ወርቅ፡ ንግስትየ፡ ወለተ፡ ዳዊት፡ ንጉሥ።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a11">
                                    <locus from="178v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT2833RepCh117" type="complete"/>. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ምሉዓ፡ ሞገስ፡ ወጸጋ።
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a12">
                                    <locus from="179v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <title ref="LIT3064RepCh344" type="complete"/>. The following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">እሴብሕ፡ ጸጋኪ፡ ኦምልእተ፡ ጸጋ፡ ወእትጋነይ፡ ለኪ፡ ኦምልእተ፡ ውዳሴ፡
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a13">
                                    <locus from="180r" to="180rc"/>
                                    <desc type="Unclear">Possibly a land grant. The writing in <locus target="#180rc"/> has been erased, except the last six lines.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">በጸሎታ፡ ወበስእለ<sic resp="PRS10171Wright">ተ</sic>፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ተሣሀለነ፡ እግዚኦ፤
                                        ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ አእላፍ፡ ሰገድ፡ ዘወሀቡ፡ ለስልጣነ፡ ከርስቶስ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡  ሎቱ፡ ምድረ፡ መስቀል፡ ፪መዓረ፡ ዘዘ ስቀል፡ ወዘዮ፤፤ <gap reason="omitted" resp="PRS10171Wright"/>
                                        <del rend="erasure"/> ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ <persName ref="PRS10375Yohanne#n3">አእላፍ፡ ሰገድ፡</persName> ዘወሀቡ፡ ለስልጣነ፡ ከርስቶስ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩን፡
                                        ሎቱ፡ ምድረ፡ መስቀል፡ ፪መዓረ፡ ዘዘመስቀል፡ ወዘዮ፤፤</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a14">
                                    <locus from="180v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">
                              <foreign xml:lang="am">Maṣḥaf za-ḫʷǝlqʷ marhočč</foreign> for <foreign xml:lang="gez">Maskaram</foreign>
                                    and <foreign xml:lang="gez">Ṭǝqǝmt</foreign>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am">መጽሐፍ፡ ዘኍልቍ፡ መርሆች፡</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <locus from="6r"/>
                                    <desc>The names of <persName ref="PRS12260Elyas"/>, <persName ref="PRS12261Isayeyyas"/>, <persName ref="PRS12262AmataD"/> and <persName ref="PRS12263Elyud"/> occur in <ref target="#a7"/>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
